/i/ec3npyj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fec3npyj.jpg&h=648ef6a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好唔記得831幫警甴殘殺手足兇手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YJzPCRN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYJzPCRN.jpg&h=f8ccc6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n突發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CZuNAtv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCZuNAtv.png&h=a8f19de6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不反都出埋唔好再搵藉口唔出<br />\n1月1號維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/snowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n【元旦大遊行　不反已出】<br />\n<br />\n民陣已收到警方發出的不反對通知書，<br />\n可以正式同各位講多次，1.1 維園見！<br />\n<br />\n元旦遊行當日將會有超過 40 個新成立工會同大家見面，歡迎大家瞭解詳情，加入你所屬行業的工會，壯大抗爭的組織力量。<br />\n<br />\n毋忘承諾，並肩同行，五大訴求，缺一不可，<br />\n一月一，維園見！<br />\n<br />\n【民陣元旦大遊行】<br />\n2020.1.1 星期三 Wednesday｜2PM<br />\n維園中央草坪 遊行至 遮打道行人專用區<br />\nFrom Victoria Park (Central Lawn) to <br />\nChater Road Pedestrian Precinct<br />\n<br />\n*已取得不反對通知書<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Received"},{"pid":"848f5d9ce8a0697a8e4ee3d4e6cdf0ed614a12be","tid":1805590,"uid":271516,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T16:56:47.000Z","msg":"差少少又盲眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"527491d6f0e09542d33f22c37703abef789a7c49","tid":1805590,"uid":263878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T16:57:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好有事"},{"pid":"7c43ca88af6f58af8d58821e93662fcf26c61172","tid":1805590,"uid":5995,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T16:58:28.000Z","msg":"鄧小巧家姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"